binson]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[\u00c9velyne Terras]] || 6\u20130, 6\u20132\n|-style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss  ||1968 || [[1968 Australian Championships|Australian Championships]]  || Grass ||  {{flagicon|AUS}} Judy Tegart || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Karen Krantzcke]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Kerry Reid|Kerry Melville]] || 4\u20136, 6\u20133, 2\u20136\n|-style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss || 1976 || [[1976 Australian Open|Australian Open]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|TCH}} [[Ren\u00e1ta Tomanov\u00e1]] || {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Evonne Goolagong]]<br />{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Helen Gourlay]] || 1\u20138\n|-style=\"background:#ebc2af;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss ||1978 || [[1978 French Open|French Open]] || Grass || {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Gail Chanfreau|Gail Sherriff]] || {{flagicon|YUG}} [[Mima Jau\u0161ovec]]<br>{{flagicon|ROM}} [[Virginia Ruzici]] || 5\u20137, 6\u20134, 8\u20136\n|}\n\n=== Mixed doubles: 9 (4 titles, 5 runners-up)  ===\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\" \n!style=\"width:50px\"|Result\n!style=\"width:40px\"|Year\n!style=\"width:200px\"|Championship \n!style=\"width:50px\"|Surface\n!style=\"width:200px\"|Partner\n!style=\"width:200px\"|Opponents\n!style=\"width:150px\" class=\"unsortable\"|Score\n|-style=\"background:#cfc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win  || 1961 || [[1961 Wimbledon Championships|Wimbledon]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Fred Stolle]] || {{flagicon|FRG}} [[Edda Buding]] <br> {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Robert Howe (tennis)|Bob Howe]] || 11\u20139, 6\u20132\n|-style=\"background:#ffc;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Win  || 1962 || [[1962 Australian Championships|Australian Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|AUS}} Fred Stolle || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Darlene Hard]] <br> {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Roger Taylor (tennis)|Roger Taylor]] || 6\u20133, 9\u20134\n|-style=\"background:#ebc2af;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Loss  || 1962 || [[1962 French Championships (tennis)|French Championships