{"title_page": "Kalwa, Thane", "text_new": "{{Other places|Kalwa (disambiguation){{!}}Kalwa}}\n{{Refimprove|date=November 2014}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2017}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Kalwa\n| native_name                     = \n| native_name_lang                = \n| other_name                      = Kalva\n| settlement_type                 = Suburb\n| image_skyline                   = <!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:Kalwa skyline.jpeg|thumb|Kalwa skyline]] -->\n| image_alt                       = \n| image_caption                   = \n| nickname                        = \n| image_map                       = \n| map_alt                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| pushpin_map                     = Mumbai\n| pushpin_label_position          = \n| pushpin_map_alt                 = \n| pushpin_map_caption             = \n| coordinates                     = {{coord|19.19705|N|72.99853|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flagicon|IND}} [[India]]\n| subdivision_type1               = State\n| subdivision_type2               = District\n| subdivision_type3               = Taluka\n| subdivision_type4               = Metro\n| subdivision_name1               = Maharashtra\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Thane district|Thane]]\n| subdivision_name3               = [[Thane]]\n| subdivision_name4               = Thane\n| established_title               = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date                = \n| founder                         = \n| named_for                       = \n| government_type                 = Municipal Corporation\n| governing_body                  = Thane Municipal Corporation\n| unit_pref                       = Metric\n| area_footnotes                  = \n| area_total_km2                  = \n| area_rank                       = \n| elevation_footnotes             = \n| elevation_m                     = \n| population_total                = \n| population_as_of                = \n| population_density_km2          = 70 people\n| population_rank                 = \n| population_demonym              = \n| population_note                 = \n| demographics_type1              = Languages\n| demographics1_title1            = Official\n| timezone1                       = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1                     = +5:30\n| postal_code_type                = [[Postal Index Number|PIN]]\n| area_code                       = 022\n| area_code_type                  = Telephone code\n| registration_plate              = MH-04\n| blank1_name_sec1                = [[Lok Sabha]] constituency\n| blank1_info_sec1                = [[Kalyan (Lok Sabha constituency)|Kalyan]]\n| website                         = \n| footnotes                       = \n| demographics1_info1             = [[Marathi language|Marathi]]\n| blank2_name_sec1                = [[Vidhan Sabha]] constituency\n| blank2_info_sec1                = [[Mumbra-Kalwa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Mumbra-Kalwa]]\n| official_name                   = \n}}\n\n'''Kalwa''' is a part of the [[Thane district]] of the Maharashtra state in [[India]]. The nearest railway station is the [[Kalwa railway station]] on the Central Line of the [[Mumbai Suburban Railway]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/topic/Kalwa-railway-station|title=Kalwa railway station: Latest News, Videos and Photos of Kalwa railway station {{!}} Times of India|website=The Times of India|url-status=live|access-date=15 October 2019}}</ref>\n\nOn July 29, 2014, [[Kalwa railway station|Kalwa]], along with Mumbra, became first railway station in the country to get free WiFi access for commuters and general public.<ref>{{cite news|title=Kalwa, Mumbra railway stns to get free Wi-Fi|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/thane/Kalwa-Mumbra-railway-stns-to-get-free-Wi-Fi/articleshow/39184067.cms}}</ref>\n\n[[Rajiv Gandhi Medical College]] and Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Hospital, which is run by [[Thane Municipal Corporation]], is located in Kalwa.\n\nKalwa is developing along with the neighbouring areas of Kharegaon,Parsik Nagar and Manisha nagar. Construction of the 3rd Kalwa Bridge is also nearing to completion which would ease the traffic at the Kalwa Road junction where Mumbai-Pune Road and Thane Belapur Road meet.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Thane district]]\n", "text_old": "{{Other places|Kalwa (disambiguation){{!}}Kalwa}}\n{{Refimprove|date=November 2014}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=July 2017}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name                            = Kalwa\n| native_name                     = \n| native_name_lang                = \n| other_name                      = Kalva\n| settlement_type                 = Suburb\n| image_skyline                   = <!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:Kalwa skyline.jpeg|thumb|Kalwa skyline]] -->\n| image_alt                       = \n| image_caption                   = \n| nickname                        = \n| image_map                       = \n| map_alt                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| pushpin_map                     = Mumbai\n| pushpin_label_position          = \n| pushpin_map_alt                 = \n| pushpin_map_caption             = \n| coordinates                     = {{coord|19.19705|N|72.99853|E|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = Country\n| subdivision_name                = {{flagicon|IND}} [[India]]\n| subdivision_type1               = State\n| subdivision_type2               = District\n| subdivision_type3               = Taluka\n| subdivision_type4               = Metro\n| subdivision_name1               = Maharashtra\n| subdivision_name2               = [[Thane district|Thane]]\n| subdivision_name3               = [[Thane]]\n| subdivision_name4               = Thane\n| established_title               = <!-- Established -->\n| established_date                = \n| founder                         = \n| named_for                       = \n| government_type                 = Municipal Corporation\n| governing_body                  = Thane Municipal Corporation\n| unit_pref                       = Metric\n| area_footnotes                  = \n| area_total_km2                  = \n| area_rank                       = \n| elevation_footnotes             = \n| elevation_m                     = \n| population_total                = \n| population_as_of                = \n| population_density_km2          = 70 people\n| population_rank                 = \n| population_demonym              = \n| population_note                 = \n| demographics_type1              = Languages\n| demographics1_title1            = Official\n| timezone1                       = [[Indian Standard Time|IST]]\n| utc_offset1                     = +5:30\n| postal_code_type                = [[Postal Index Number|PIN]]\n| area_code                       = 022\n| area_code_type                  = Telephone code\n| registration_plate              = MH-04\n| blank1_name_sec1                = [[Lok Sabha]] constituency\n| blank1_info_sec1                = [[Kalyan (Lok Sabha constituency)|Kalyan]]\n| website                         = \n| footnotes                       = \n| demographics1_info1             = [[Marathi language|Marathi]]\n| blank2_name_sec1                = [[Vidhan Sabha]] constituency\n| blank2_info_sec1                = [[Mumbra-Kalwa (Vidhan Sabha constituency)|Mumbra-Kalwa]]\n| official_name                   = \n}}\n\n'''Kalwa''' is a part of the [[Thane district]] of the Maharashtra state in [[India]]. The nearest railway station is the [[Kalwa railway station]] on the Central Line of the [[Mumbai Suburban Railway]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/topic/Kalwa-railway-station|title=Kalwa railway station: Latest News, Videos and Photos of Kalwa railway station {{!}} Times of India|website=The Times of India|url-status=live|access-date=15 October 2019}}</ref>\n\nOn July 29, 2014, [[Kalwa railway station|Kalwa]], along with Mumbra, became first railway station in the country to get free WiFi access for commuters and general public.<ref>{{cite news|title=Kalwa, Mumbra railway stns to get free Wi-Fi|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/thane/Kalwa-Mumbra-railway-stns-to-get-free-Wi-Fi/articleshow/39184067.cms}}</ref>\n\n[[Rajiv Gandhi Medical College]] and Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Hospital, which is run by [[Thane Municipal Corporation]], is located in Kalwa.\n\nKalwa is developing along with the neighbouring areas of Kharegaon and Parsik Nagar. Construction of the 3rd Kalwa Bridge is also nearing to completion which would ease the traffic at the Kalwa Road junction where Mumbai-Pune Road and Thane Belapur Road meet.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Thane district]]\n", "name_user": "Saurabh khandzode", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(Developing areas of Kalwa)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kalwa,_Thane"}
